{"tid":2257300,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 搶先釋出 13 首新歌亮點片段　上一首主打〈More & More〉MV 也破兩億啦！","createTime":"2020-10-25T04:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T13:36:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dfac419018a133e74c60aa7d003defd6006071f7","tid":2257300,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_cd8d9c48fb79b5dbb90229d9ebe70466/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-25/131146-881762.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_cd8d9c48fb79b5dbb90229d9ebe70466%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-25%2F131146-881762.png&h=c9e068e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明天 TWICE 就會帶著有許多成員參與創作的全新正規專輯〈Eyes wide open〉回歸，光聽亮點集錦就等不及啦！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（25 日）公開了 TWICE 第三張正規專輯〈Eyes wide open〉的亮點試聽影片，從主打歌 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 開始一路公開 &ldquo;Hell in Heaven&rdquo;、&rdquo;Up No More&rdquo;、&rdquo;Do What We Like&rdquo;、&ldquo;Bring it Back&rdquo;、&ldquo;Believer&rdquo;⋯⋯等 13 首歌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VZjiZZVL5eY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVZjiZZVL5eY&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4660615c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VZjiZZVL5eY</a><br />\n〈Eyes wide open〉不僅嘗試了豐富的曲風，凸顯出 TWICE 令人驚喜的聲音表現，其中多首歌皆由成員獨立作詞，從各方面而言，這張專輯都是徹底呈現 TWICE 色彩的代表作。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，在 TWICE 將於 26 日發行新專輯前夕，她們的上一首主打歌 &ldquo;More &amp; More&rdquo; MV 觀看次數也在昨天跨越了兩億大關！"},{"pid":"b873c08a84310cb8c4f3acf68e98c49ac60a5b45","tid":2257300,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"Twice回歸大發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6c3a7e500130478e3c6824b38e5031f2cfee87","tid":2257300,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b873c08a84310cb8c4f3acf68e98c49ac60a5b4